    Hello All, 

    Please be informed that with immediate effect this account will not have any sign-off block, but just a form field for "eSignature" at the end of the report.   This will appear as a space when you are processing nonVRS jobs on MTC, do not delete this "space."




    Floating ID will appear as usual (i.e., like before and you will need to manually put in the physician name

    For VRS jobs it will be take care of in the backend.

    AI has been updated with this information.
